Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
LOCATION
Bellevue is an established suburb located in the eastern suburbs of Perth, approximately 20km away from the Perth CBD and ideally only 10km aware from the Perth Airports with the main access routes being Row Highway and Great Eastern Highway.  The area has a large industrial and commercial zone with a mixture of old and new infrastructure in place.

KEY FEATURES

- 2 storey office of 240sqm* with reverse cycle air condition NBN and covered parking
- 409sqm* of workshop
- Wash bay and work pit in the workshop
- 3 phase power to the workshop
- Clean room
- Zoned “industrial”
- 3 street frontage and access
- Statutory outgoings $27,330* per annum plus GST

*approx

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Can be leased separately or together
